*Tiho* se spuštala uz stepenice. (She descended the stairs quietly.)

*Tiho* se smejala. (She laughed quietly.)

*Tihi* šumovi dolazili su iz daljine. (Quiet noises were coming from a distance.)

*Tihoća* je bila prekrasna. (The stillness was beautiful.)

*Tiha* noć je prekrivena zvezdama. (The silent night was filled with stars.)

*Tiho* kucanje na vratima je upozoravalo. (The soft knocking on the door was a warning.)

*Tiha* reka je tekla kroz šumu. (The silent river flowed through the woods.)

*Tiho* se razgovaralo u sobi. (People were talking quietly in the room.)